content:
**Ahoy Sailors, here are the the last few weeks of changes. 8/24 - 9/4
Future postings will be more regular to keep you informed of all the different facets of the server. **

fields.name: Free prisons weekend
fields.value: - 9/4 to 9/6 take advantage of our VIP exclusive game mode!

fields.name: New Main Lobby
fields.value: - Come experience our new main Dragon Lobby

fields.name: New Game Maps
fields.value:
- Two new survival multiplayer maps

**New Skywars Lucky Block duos map with lucky block updates:**
  -  - Western
  -  - Heaven

**New Skywars Lucky Block quads map:**
  -  - Site
  -  - Fantasy
  -  - Fairytail

fields.name: New waiting lobbys
fields.value:
- Capture the flag
- Zombie Apocalypse
- Skywars
- Bedwars

fields.name: Changes to the cactus meta
fields.value:
- Made the pop off trajectory of cactus more consistent
- Cactus growth timing made more random
- Improved cactus farm performance

fields.name: Enchants disable
fields.value:
- Disabled enchants for survival 
- Removed enchanting table from prisons
